I have to preface my review by saying that I haven't actually climbed at Focus, but my son attended a competition here.  I can say that the front desk was organized and seemed to have their stuff together.  The gym itself has a combination of bouldering and roped climbing though most of the gym appeared to be dedicated to bouldering.  All around good experience for us on an early Saturday morning.

